00:25:02,568 --> 00:25:05,070
Life is difficult.

279
00:25:05,571 --> 00:25:06,638
Have you felt that?

280
00:25:44,843 --> 00:25:46,412
These are the carrots
that daddy eats every day.

281
00:25:46,478 --> 00:25:47,980
And the fried egg that mommy loves.

282
00:25:53,152 --> 00:25:54,520
I'm overjoyed.

283
00:25:55,354 --> 00:25:57,656
To be able to have breakfast
cooked by Shancai.

284
00:25:59,124 --> 00:26:00,692
It doesn't have to be stir-fried carrots.

285
00:26:00,759 --> 00:26:03,128
I'll even take raw carrots.

286
00:26:03,962 --> 00:26:05,064
You can treat me like a rabbit.

287
00:26:05,130 --> 00:26:06,165
I'll gnaw carrots every day.

288
00:26:06,532 --> 00:26:07,833
Let's eat.

289
00:26:17,076 --> 00:26:18,844
Mom, what's wrong?

290
00:26:21,246 --> 00:26:24,383
We are actually very worried about you.

291
00:26:25,317 --> 00:26:28,487
We watch you leave home early
and come home late every day, working.

292
00:26:29,588 --> 00:26:32,291
You're upset.

293
00:26:32,357 --> 00:26:34,193
At night, you will hide
in your bedroom crying.

294
00:26:35,094 --> 00:26:37,963
We will hide in our bedroom crying too.

295
00:26:38,630 --> 00:26:40,833
I don't know what to do,

296
00:26:41,133 --> 00:26:43,268
so I went to the temple and worship.

297
00:26:43,535 --> 00:26:44,369
Cast moon blocks.

298
00:26:45,270 --> 00:26:48,507
Why is my daughter's life so hard?

299
00:26:48,574 --> 00:26:50,909
Mom, I'm all right.

300
00:26:53,312 --> 00:26:54,746
That's right.

301
00:26:54,813 --> 00:26:56,315
It's all right.

302
00:26:56,381 --> 00:26:57,549
We are all alright.

303
00:26:58,984 --> 00:27:00,185
You see.

304
00:27:00,252 --> 00:27:02,621
My car selling business
is getting better now.

305
00:27:03,455 --> 00:27:05,657
And Shancai has pulled herself together.

306
00:27:05,724 --> 00:27:08,494
As long as we are happy
together every day,

307
00:27:08,560 --> 00:27:11,396
nothing will stop us, right?

308
00:27:13,398 --> 00:27:14,299
As long as I'm happy,

309
00:27:15,167 --> 00:27:16,068
Shancai is happy.

310
00:27:16,135 --> 00:27:17,236
As long as Shancai is happy,

311
00:27:17,302 --> 00:27:18,971
your mother is happy.

312
00:27:19,404 --> 00:27:21,840
We... will all be happy.

313
00:27:22,174 --> 00:27:24,209
Let's eat.

314
00:27:24,276 --> 00:27:25,911
We will be happy.

315
00:27:38,524 --> 00:27:39,458
Guys...

316
00:27:40,659 --> 00:27:43,028
From today,
Master Ximen will take on the role

317
00:27:44,163 --> 00:27:47,132
of business promotion manager.

318
00:27:47,966 --> 00:27:49,935
Everybody must do their best

319
00:27:50,969 --> 00:27:52,504
to assist Master Ximen.

320
00:27:52,871 --> 00:27:56,842
You must learn how things work
in the corporation the fastest you can.

321
00:27:58,076 --> 00:27:59,811
Let's welcome Young Master Ximen.

322
00:28:01,780 --> 00:28:03,248
Looking forward to working with you.

323
00:28:04,950 --> 00:28:06,785
