330
00:28:27,940 --> 00:28:28,840
No problem...

331
00:28:29,208 --> 00:28:30,209
Yes.

332
00:28:35,347 --> 00:28:36,748
Excuse me, please hang on a moment.

333
00:28:39,151 --> 00:28:40,419
