335
00:28:43,088 --> 00:28:45,324
I'm Xu Shaoyang
from the business department.

336
00:28:45,824 --> 00:28:47,125
Xu Shaoyang.

337
00:28:47,759 --> 00:28:48,894
You'll be my secretary.

338
00:28:49,628 --> 00:28:50,629
Is that all right?

339
00:28:50,696 --> 00:28:51,663
Me?

340
00:28:51,997 --> 00:28:52,998
Of course.

341
00:28:57,002 --> 00:28:58,103
Come in, master.

342
00:29:05,477 --> 00:29:07,746
