353
00:29:26,498 --> 00:29:28,166
I was wrong, I'm sorry.

354
00:29:29,301 --> 00:29:32,104
Please show me
the marketing plan for this season.

355
00:29:32,170 --> 00:29:33,405
And later at 2:00 p.m,

356
00:29:33,472 --> 00:29:35,440
