department. We'll have a meeting.

357
00:29:35,507 --> 00:29:37,175
-Today?
-Is there a problem?

358
00:29:38,243 --> 00:29:40,445
Young Master... I mean, Manager.

359
00:29:40,512 --> 00:29:41,713
