-Please.

369
00:31:30,655 --> 00:31:35,060
Wow, it feels so good.

370
00:31:35,961 --> 00:31:37,529
I haven't come to the beach
for a long time.

371
00:31:38,997 --> 00:31:40,499
Remember the time we went to Okinawa?

372
00:31:40,766 --> 00:31:41,767
Of course.

373
00:31:41,833 --> 00:31:43,335
Both you and Ximen came with hot girls.

374
00:31:44,102 --> 00:31:45,637
-Did we?
-You did.

375
00:31:45,704 --> 00:31:47,406
They all have perfect curves.

376
00:31:47,472 --> 00:31:48,907
