377
00:31:48,974 --> 00:31:50,108
And you also--

378
00:31:50,175 --> 00:31:51,777
We saw Ah Si.

379
00:31:52,677 --> 00:31:53,779
Where?

380
00:31:56,348 --> 00:31:57,315
At the pub.

381
00:31:57,716 --> 00:31:58,750
Where is he now?

382
00:32:00,285 --> 00:32:01,486
He fought for us.

383
00:32:01,553 --> 00:32:02,954
And then he ran away.

384
00:32:03,555 --> 00:32:04,990
We couldn't catch up with him.

385
00:32:08,260 --> 00:32:09,895
He really doesn't remember anything.

386
00:32:11,096 --> 00:32:12,864
From afar, I saw him
in his ragged T-shirt,

387
00:32:12,931 --> 00:32:14,332
worn-out jeans,

388
00:32:14,733 --> 00:32:16,067
his expression,

389
00:32:17,369 --> 00:32:18,203
and his attitude.

390
00:32:20,572 --> 00:32:21,740
Suddenly, I got scared.

391
00:32:22,707 --> 00:32:23,642
Of what?

392
00:32:23,975 --> 00:32:25,577
He didn't want to go back
to the past at all.

393
00:32:26,344 --> 00:32:27,979
He only wants to live his present life.

394
00:32:33,652 --> 00:32:34,920
So, is he doing great now?

395
00:32:38,089 --> 00:32:38,924
Maybe.

396
00:32:42,427 --> 00:32:43,528
Then, I'm at ease.

397
00:32:44,262 --> 00:32:47,432
Shancai, are you not worried
that Ah Si will never come back?

398
00:32:48,033 --> 00:32:49,134
What for?

399
00:32:50,202 --> 00:32:51,603
Not even you could catch up with him.

400
00:32:55,540 --> 00:32:57,409
The moment Ah Si stood before us,

401
00:32:57,809 --> 00:32:59,411
I had a strange feeling.

402
00:33:00,846 --> 00:33:03,548
A part of me was envious of him.

403
00:33:04,749 --> 00:33:05,851
He lost his memory,

404
00:33:05,917 --> 00:33:07,752
and his identity.

405
00:33:07,819 --> 00:33:08,954
However,

406
00:33:09,020 --> 00:33:11,022
he's found a new life.

407
00:33:12,491 --> 00:33:13,658
Do you know?

408
00:33:13,725 --> 00:33:15,360
Two days later, I'll be putting on a suit,

409
00:33:15,427 --> 00:33:16,828
and a necktie,

410
00:33:16,895 --> 00:33:18,063
and start a boring life

411
00:33:18,129 --> 00:33:20,198
where I punch in and out
when I go to and leave work.

412
00:33:20,599 --> 00:33:22,267
Can you imagine me like that?

413
00:33:23,935 --> 00:33:25,070
You must look very handsome.

414
00:33:27,672 --> 00:33:28,874
Of course.

415
00:33:30,542 --> 00:33:32,143
But I don't want to become
someone like that.

416
00:33:34,312 --> 00:33:35,480
Actually...

417
00:33:36,114 --> 00:33:38,450
This is just what the world is like.

418
00:33:38,517 --> 00:33:42,153
