by the chef for Chinese Valentine's Day.

500
00:38:20,565 --> 00:38:21,399
Right.

501
00:38:21,466 --> 00:38:23,368
Chinese Valentine's Day is two days away.

502
00:38:24,435 --> 00:38:27,839
I wonder if they could attract customers,
to promote the sales.

503
00:38:28,339 --> 00:38:31,209
There weren't so many holidays
going on in the past.

504
00:38:32,343 --> 00:38:35,580
Good thing is, young people nowadays
are too emotional,

505
00:38:35,647 --> 00:38:37,582
which brings us
a lot of business opportunities.

506
00:38:37,982 --> 00:38:42,487
But the student employees all chose
to take leaves on Valentine's Day.

507
00:38:42,554 --> 00:38:44,656
