509
00:38:47,692 --> 00:38:48,760
Can you do that?

510
00:38:49,794 --> 00:38:50,628
But...

511
00:38:50,695 --> 00:38:53,331
Your tall, handsome boyfriend.

512
00:38:53,398 --> 00:38:54,933
Isn't he taking you anywhere to celebrate?

513
00:38:57,168 --> 00:38:58,937
If two people can be together,

514
00:38:59,003 --> 00:39:00,405
every day is Valentine's Day.

515
00:39:00,471 --> 00:39:01,439
