516
00:39:01,973 --> 00:39:04,108
Well, okay, that's a deal.

517
00:39:04,175 --> 00:39:06,911
I'll pay you double on that day.

518
00:39:07,278 --> 00:39:08,613
Thank you, ma'am.

519
00:39:08,680 --> 00:39:09,681
You're welcome.

520
00:39:09,747 --> 00:39:11,549
